{
  "text": "The instrument would like for me to ask if there is any problem with her kidneys? I am Ra. This query is more complex than its brevity certifies. The physical complex renal system of this instrument is much damaged. The time/space equivalent which rules the body complex is without flaw. There was a serious question, due to psychic attack, as to whether the spiritual healing of this system would endure. It did so but has the need to be re-enforced by affirmation of the ascendancy of the spiritual over the apparent or visible. When this instrument began ingesting substances designed to heal, in a physical sense, among other things the renal complex, this instrument was ceasing the affirmation of healing. Due to this, again, the healing was weakened. This is of some profound distortion and it would be well for the instrument to absorb these concepts. We ask your forgiveness for offering information which may abridge free will, but the dedication of the instrument is such that it would persevere regardless of its condition, if possible. Thusly we offer this information that it may persevere with a fuller distortion towards comfort.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "The instrument would like for me to ask if there is any problem with her kidneys?",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 81,
        "start": 2.28,
        "end": 18.801
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 82,
        "end_offset": 90,
        "start": 18.821,
        "end": 18.961
      },
      {
        "segment": "This query is more complex than its brevity certifies.",
        "start_offset": 91,
        "end_offset": 145,
        "start": 21.681,
        "end": 38.382
      },
      {
        "segment": "The physical complex renal system of this instrument is much damaged.",
        "start_offset": 146,
        "end_offset": 215,
        "start": 42.543,
        "end": 64.044
      },
      {
        "segment": "The time/space equivalent which rules the body complex is without flaw.",
        "start_offset": 216,
        "end_offset": 287,
        "start": 67.744,
        "end": 92.946
      },
      {
        "segment": "There was a serious question, due to psychic attack, as to whether the spiritual healing of this system would endure.",
        "start_offset": 288,
        "end_offset": 405,
        "start": 98.206,
        "end": 141.049
      },
      {
        "segment": "It did so but has the need to be re-enforced by affirmation of the ascendancy of the spiritual over the apparent or visible.",
        "start_offset": 406,
        "end_offset": 530,
        "start": 145.109,
        "end": 187.372
      },
      {
        "segment": "When this instrument began ingesting substances designed to heal, in a physical sense, among other things the renal complex, this instrument was ceasing the affirmation of healing.",
        "start_offset": 531,
        "end_offset": 711,
        "start": 190.512,
        "end": 241.736
      },
      {
        "segment": "Due to this, again, the healing was weakened.",
        "start_offset": 712,
        "end_offset": 757,
        "start": 245.296,
        "end": 256.797
      },
      {
        "segment": "This is of some profound distortion and it would be well for the instrument to absorb these concepts.",
        "start_offset": 758,
        "end_offset": 859,
        "start": 258.577,
        "end": 290.819
      },
      {
        "segment": "We ask your forgiveness for offering information which may abridge free will, but the dedication of the instrument is such that it would persevere regardless of its condition, if possible.",
        "start_offset": 860,
        "end_offset": 1048,
        "start": 293.079,
        "end": 346.722
      },
      {
        "segment": "Thusly we offer this information that it may persevere with a fuller distortion towards comfort.",
        "start_offset": 1049,
        "end_offset": 1145,
        "start": 349.383,
        "end": 381.885
      }
    ],
